parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause inaccurate or stuck speedometer readings, faulty gauge readings, and warning lights to remain illuminated, which can lead to accidents, confusion, or inconvenience while driving.
symptoms: Speedometer sticks or displays inaccurate speeds
other gauges on the instrument panel give no/false readings
warning lights remain illuminated
instrument panel display fades from the inside of the light housing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag light to remain on, indicating a potential safety risk, which can lead to accidents or injuries if the airbag does not deploy properly in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag light remains on
no collision or incident occurred to trigger the light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause difficulties in fueling the vehicle, leading to inconvenience, wasted time, and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Fuel pump only allows small amounts of fuel to be pumped
gas spills out while fueling
fuel tank was not overfilled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various warning lights to remain illuminated, the ignition to get stuck, and the vehicle to continue running even when turned off, leading to potential safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: Warning lights remain illuminated
ignition gets stuck
vehicle continues running even when turned off
burning wire smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can cause a lack of warning to other drivers or pedestrians, leading to potential safety risks.
symptoms: Horn fails to sound when needed
horn failure occurs after a period of non-use.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gear Shift Lever Position Indicator Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shift lever position indicator can cause the driver to be unsure of the vehicle's gear position, leading to potential accidents or difficulty operating the vehicle.
symptoms: The gear shift lever position indicator light fails to illuminate
making it difficult to determine the vehicle's gear position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, decelerate, or become difficult to control, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to shift into gear
the transmission fluid level is low
the transmission active indicator light comes on
the vehicle decelerates or coasts
and the driver loses control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear differential failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: The rear differential locks
causing the vehicle to lose control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag system fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag system deploys incorrectly
the instrument cluster displays incorrect information
the fuel gauge fluctuates
and abnormal noises emit from the wheels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corroded front brake lines can cause a sudden loss of brake fluid, leading to a complete brake failure, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake failure warning lights on the dashboard
large pool of brake fluid under the vehicle
leak from one of the brake pipes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the emergency/parking brake release mechanism can cause the brake to engage unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Broken emergency/parking brake release mechanism
brake engages unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Separation of the emergency brake friction linings from their metal shoe can cause complete failure of the emergency brake, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Complete failure of the emergency brake
ruined rotor and brake pads of the rear brakes.
